dc_description_s: This line data layer represents roads for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Dane_MPO_Roads_2014.gdb, These road centerlines are published by the City of Madison-Metropolitan Planning Organization (MPO) and may differ from the roads data published by the Dane County Land Information Office.
dc_creator_sm: City of Madison - Metropolitan Planning Organization (MPO)
